[15:37:44     1] The code contains two kinds of functions: implementation functions and FFI entry points. A function is an FFI entry point if it has the `#[no_mangle]` or `#[export_name]` attribute ("export attributes"). Note that just having `unsafe extern "C"` qualifiers without export attributes does NOT make a function an FFI entry point. All functions without export attributes are implementation functions.
