[15:37:44     1] - Eliminate calls to FFI imports and other unsafe functions. Try to replace these with suitable safe Rust operations, e.g. `printf` -> `println!`.
[15:37:44     1] - Remove the `unsafe` qualifier from functions that no longer need it, so that their callers can be made safe.
