[15:40:16    63]  - `cJSON_New_Item` still contains the hook allocation/raw write boundary. Do not remove custom hooks or switch this to plain `Box` unless hook behavior is preserved for FFI-created items.
[15:40:16    63]  - Do not change string/raw creator allocation order casually: allocating the item before duplicating the string preserves cleanup behavior with custom hooks.
